<heading>show - Show world details.</heading>

<rule/>

<heading level="2">
Usage
</heading>

<pre>
  show NAME
</pre>

<heading level="2">
Description
</heading>

<paragraph>
Displays details of a specific world: ID, name, description
and entry box.
</paragraph>

<heading level="2">
Examples
</heading>

<pre>
show Work
  Show details of the world called Work.
</pre>

<heading level="2">
See also
</heading>

<paragraph>
add, delete, edit, list
</paragraph>
